'''Slingball''' was a type of sport involving teams and the passing of balls on a court. Injuries were common. The [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] of [[Champion Squadron]] in [[General/Legends|General]] [[Horton Salm/Legends|Horton Salm's]] [[Defender Wing]] liked to play slingball.

